msgid ""
"method used in the denoising core.\n"
"non-local means works best for `lightness' blending,\n"
"wavelets work best for `color' blending"
msgstr ""
"način koji se koristi za uklanjanje šuma.\n"
"nelokalizovani proseci radi bolje kod stapanja svetline,\n"
"niskotalasni radi bolje kod stapanja boja"

